column2: select top # S.ObjID, S.z, #, L1.ew, L1.ewErr, L1.continuum #, L_OIII.ew, L_OIII.ewErr, L_OIII.continuum #, L_OIII.ew, L_OIII.ewErr, L_OIII.continuum FROM SpecPhoto AS S JOIN SpecLine AS L1 ON S.SpecObjID = L1.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L_OIII ON S.SpecObjID = L_OIII.SpecObjID WHERE (specclass = # or specclass = #) and L1.LineId = # and L_OIII.LineId = # and L_OIII.LineId = # and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .#
